data.title: Buchanan, Natalie Reviews & Portfolio
data.meta_description: Buchanan, Natalie is a Celebrant based in Peregian Springs serving multiple regions. View profile, customer reviews, portfolio and enquire today.
data.text: At EventZen I'm all about connection, authenticity and most importantly LOVE! With over 20 years experience, EventZen provides affordable Planning, Styling and Event Management and Celebrant services! I pride myself on being a down to earth, authentic, fun and creative person, who wants you to have a stress free enjoyable experience planning your big event! From weddings and milestone birthdays, to cocktail parties and intimate dinner parties; I take your fun seriously and offer creative design, complete or partial planning and flawless execution. Get in touch for an obligation free chat! "As a Wedding Planner, I've had years of experience helping couples plan and coordinate their big day. It made sense to take the next steps to become a Celebrant. Depending on when we connect, as a planner I spend anywhere from 1-18 months with my clients and we build a connection, trust and often friendships in that time. The opportunity to be their Celebrant and marry them on their wedding day, is the cherry on top!"
